Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:08.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我和阿三哥在一起之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也會變得成熟嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.44,0:00:23.55,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一道曙光！看不到第一道曙光！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:25.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明等了這麼久！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:28.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 阿柳 打草驚蛇了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:33.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是那個嗎 那道曙光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.79,0:00:35.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 在那座建築物的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:39.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說看見太陽的時候不就是新年的日出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.84,0:00:43.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,從地平線出現的時候才是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:45.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,水谷同學 你也太嚴格了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啊 因為不好好定義的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:51.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不知道今年的第一次日出是看到還是沒看到…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:52.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:56.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那裏出現的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:00:58.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就叫做第一次日出 也可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.30,0:01:02.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但說到底 地平線也看不見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:06.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼妥協方式讓人這麼不痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:09.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫　不要在意這些小事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:11.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個就是我們等的新年日出啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.42,0:01:12.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是大樓日出
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:14.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說新年日出了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.74,0:01:17.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能日出我也還是第一次看見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:21.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 我的話不管怎樣每年都有看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:22.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,被你這麼一說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能還真沒看過 日出什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.09,0:01:26.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是第一次看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有看過日出的人還蠻多的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:34.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 夏目他們也許也沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:46.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,都到了不能和大家一起瘋的年紀了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:49.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,太陽比我想像的還要大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:51.14,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:52.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.03,0:01:54.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.93,0:01:57.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.77,0:02:02.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,些微小事我都會覺得超開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.10,0:02:06.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,明年的時候能再和大家一起來看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:51.00,tk-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs140\c&H0000AF&\frz18.12\pos(240,171)}春
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:51.00,tk-title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(315,259)}天\N將至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱鬧的新年結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.43,0:03:56.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於回到了平靜的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親和弟弟兩人都在奶奶家裏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有比這個更好的學習環境了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:04.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:09.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想安心下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:11.41,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想有信心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.13,0:04:13.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.42,0:04:15.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:22.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,元旦以後就沒有見過春了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:25.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不在意的話 那是騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:29.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在春他在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.27,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻聽了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:42.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫 在的話就快點回答啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:43.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是怎麼了 春？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.80,0:04:44.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:45.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.50,0:04:46.81,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找它
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.82,0:04:47.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有看見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.61,0:04:52.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,就稍微離開了會 就不知道跑到哪裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 春 你先冷靜下來慢慢說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:57.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 這個還是保密中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:00.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是令人著急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.29,0:05:01.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春 到底發生了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:06.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫 抱歉 現在沒有多餘的時間陪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:10.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜 吃年糕會胖的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.77,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在急什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:30.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.96,0:05:34.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什…什麼 怎麼了啊 穿成這個樣子 春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有沒有看見
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:38.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裏都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在找什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.33,0:05:42.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:43.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:45.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:47.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是一目瞭然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:49.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉了 夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.20,0:05:53.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在沒有空閒陪你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:56.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之發現了的話 就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:58.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有你的博客一直都有錯別字哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 網？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:05.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.81,0:06:08.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,詳細的內容我就不說了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:11.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之發現了就告訴我吧 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒子要正確運用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那個是葷段子？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:43.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿佐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:46.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 水谷同學 怎麼會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個電話是剛才春落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:52.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.63,0:06:54.62,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛吉田來學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:57.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道為什麼他樣子有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:07:00.34,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像在找些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.06,0:07:05.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許對春來說是個大問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一般人看來可能算不上嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:10.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣倒還好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.25,0:07:12.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊社團活動剛剛結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:15.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在去把吉田落下的潛水鏡送過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,水谷同學打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:26.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 這不是又成長了一步嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:28.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷疤是男人的勳章啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過是闌尾炎 你們在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:35.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你口吐白沫的倒下 我都不知道怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:37.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,到測量體溫的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:39.15,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦 讓二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.33,0:07:40.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:43.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:45.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看望已經結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:48.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐測吧 是姐姐來測的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:49.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:07:58.69,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.85,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己進來嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(550,147)}致春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(694,276)}我稍微出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(760,374)}晚上回來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,750)\fs50\frz10.99\c&H222424&\3c&HEFF4F3&\fn方正卡通简体\b1\pos(678,518)}自己隨便吃點東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:16.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:19.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小水 你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:23.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 我只是把春忘記的手機送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:27.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是剛剛遇見了春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像在找些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:35.91,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春同學的行為比以前還要難以理解 有一點擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.81,0:08:37.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿三哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:40.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好像出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:42.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:43.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,門沒鎖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:44.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:46.19,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是粗心大意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.32,0:08:48.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學還要留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:52.74,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是的 反正我也沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:56.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那等春回來的時候幫我交給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你要回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.34,0:09:03.56,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在學習 而且還有想在今天做完的問題集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:08.25,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的寒假 當面給春比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:12.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他什麼時候回來 留在這只會浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:15.65,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我是個閒人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.46,0:09:17.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:18.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:19.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:27.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學 你遇到什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:30.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 什 什麼事 為什麼這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼事的話就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:36.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我應該沒什麼變化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:38.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是發燒了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:03.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是讓二得闌尾炎的話不是很糟糕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.36,0:10:04.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我們總是和他在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來 我肚子也有點痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:11.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:14.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個徹底搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.16,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡  沒有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊 春
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:31.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們幾個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:34.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近有野豬 你們也小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人哪裏好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:01.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:04.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學？怎麼是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.46,0:11:08.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛小水把手機送來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:10.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:12.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:14.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太明白你的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學也來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:24.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 阿佐怎麼也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.23,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田來社團的時候一副很慌亂的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.31,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:34.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也見到吉田了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:40.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在尋找些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:46.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了小水他還能找什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:49.70,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然本人說要學習就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們買點果汁什麼的可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:56.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在自動販賣機的話沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能玩遊戲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:01.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在別人家隨便用電不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們又不知道配電盤在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:34.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(302,408,302,670)\fs50\c&H302F2B&\3c&HFEFEFE&\fn方正大黑简体\pos(302,408)}我撿到了雞~(·∑·)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(123,566,123,670)\fs50\c&H302F2B&\3c&HFEFEFE&\fn方正大黑简体\pos(123,566)}優
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:44.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小優？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:46.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你撿到的那隻雞…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:49.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這隻雞有名字什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 名古屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:17.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我在一起很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.06,0:13:35.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.54,0:13:51.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 我好像迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:56.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,在路口是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,過路口之後的道路左邊是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好 小優同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:11.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦 阿佐 我們幾個先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:15.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 再見 我們再等一會吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,說來怎麼還不回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:18.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早的聯誼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.37,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:21.47,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 店不是打烊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你們怎麼來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:30.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是阿佐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:40.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 夏目同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為什麼你們會來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.25,0:14:45.64,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:48.29,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春那個笨蛋把這個落下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.39,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們特意給送過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:03.05,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說來吉田正為了找名古屋而到處徘徊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.44,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田當時是什麼樣子的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:07.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,渾身又濕又髒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.33,0:15:10.01,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不是尋找小雞的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春同學現在在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:16.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在超越人類想像的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:18.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到山裏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.97,0:15:20.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們現在怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:25.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先要找到春田同學告訴他名古屋回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定很擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.93,0:15:29.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要去哪找他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:37.17,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 不要在意我 請繼續討論
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:41.19,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他也許在河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:41.94,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:45.40,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,渾身濕透 捕魚網
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:49.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,來我家的時候身上還沾著只長在河邊的草
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:52.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為什麼要到那裏去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:54.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點我也不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:58.58,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:02.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,山賢 你要回去了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:06.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,白癡才會陪你們一起找春 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是 那我們也回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.99,0:16:15.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊什麼啊 明明是春同學的朋友 卻這麼冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:18.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你們 我們幾個去找就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:20.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:22.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.32,0:16:24.54,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小…小水？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:27.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 小夏目要去找嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:31.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是當然了 就算只剩下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦 山賢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.61,0:16:37.52,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偶爾也應該有點人情味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:39.89,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那山賢同學補習班再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:54.26,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見 我家從這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:01.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:08.61,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.94,0:17:16.18,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼山賢同學會走到這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:19.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,天知道 原因很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.86,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 山賢同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:29.81,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大馬路應該在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:35.93,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷路的話 老老實實說出來不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才沒有迷路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.87,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 反正大馬路就在前面不遠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:46.45,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.33,0:17:55.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 要我幫你拿那袋米也行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 我就拿了這點東西而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.41,0:17:59.04,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 春同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:06.32,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪裏啊？快出來啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.66,0:18:08.13,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.77,0:18:12.20,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人究竟是不是來找人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經到晚上了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏目同學 你先回棒球中心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.51,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定吉田已經回去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且店長說不定也已經回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:31.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個人在會比較好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.42,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事沒事 我們繼續找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.11,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經給春同學留了電話和紙條了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:40.12,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想如果他回來的話 會和我們聯繫的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.61,0:18:42.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.57,0:18:43.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.82,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然想見他 可是沒有見面的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:59.36,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話 要一直走到河川的盡頭哦！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:02.07,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,See You Again！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.21,0:19:05.80,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,小夏目 不管你走到哪裏我都會追隨你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:08.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了的话 我来背你o(*≧▽≦)ツ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.67,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 讓二？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:15.73,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:18.68,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓二的傷口裂開了！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.69,0:19:22.50,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓二 讓二！！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.43,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,春
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:35.88,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:37.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.99,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我該問你才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.36,0:19:41.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,名古屋的話 我們已經找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.33,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在在棒球中心那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:47.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,名古屋？名古屋不見了嗎？什麼時候不見的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:49.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在找名古屋嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:52.83,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦 是蟲子 會發光的蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:54.35,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,發光的蟲子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.21,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天早上找到的 結果被它逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.53,0:20:00.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,到處找了好久 可是哪都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.00,0:20:04.46,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大冬天裏會發光的蟲子 會不會是你看錯了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的 在發光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:07.90,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,像螢火蟲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:10.22,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,螢火蟲不會在冬天裏出現吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.59,0:20:12.38,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,特別地漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:15.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才想和雫一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.49,0:20:20.72,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和你一起看的話 會變得更加更加地漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在擔心你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.79,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之我們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:29.34,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:31.95,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來好沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.34,0:20:33.66,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是大米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:38.60,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外地適合你呢 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:43.24,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他可以看起來總是那麼開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.98,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦這麼想 就會覺得他有時遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:51.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還無法追趕上他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.53,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法從容地接受他的那種純粹和直率
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.78,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雫！就是那個！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.36,0:21:15.08,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後查了下 說是南方有一種螢火蟲能在冬天活動
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:17.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如春所說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:20.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不能確定是不是蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.14,0:21:23.27,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,散發著美麗的光芒滑過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.63,0:21:25.06,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失在了夜空中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.13,0:21:32.92,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有許多不得不說的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:35.10,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於她的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:37.30,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.35,0:21:40.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於他的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:43.76,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於她的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:46.97,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於它的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.28,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(494,510,494,650)\fad(300,0)\fs50\c&H2F3433&\3c&HF3F5F5&\fn方正稚艺_GBK\frx32\fry0\pos(494,510)\frz358.7}您的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:54.57,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許總有一天我也能如此直率地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:22:00.75,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此坦誠地注視著身旁的他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:09.59,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 那道螢光確實看起來很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:13.71,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許 比起一個人看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:17.00,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,要漂亮得太多…太多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.82,0:23:55.48,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了 外面開始下雪了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.38,0:23:58.84,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好您好 晚上好o(*￣▽￣*)ゞ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:04.49,tk-default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…個 你是誰？
